wiki.content: "Two Princes" is a song by the New York City-based alternative rock band Spin Doctors. As a single, it reached #7 in the U.S., #2 in Canada, and #3 in the UK. It was the band's most popular song. It also ranked at #21 on Blender magazine's list of the "50 Worst Songs Ever". It ranked #41 on "VH1's 100 Greatest Songs of the 90s".
